<subSubSection id="829882825445102073A7C34025372460" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" type="distribution and taxonomic notes">
<paragraph id="C9CF7901AD909D0BEDA57A980F488ACC" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Distribution and taxonomic notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B2D3D15BA5D14655B84ED85EAA886739" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">
<taxonomicName id="12A7A8E2627A14749A2829817C679980" authorityName="Oberthuer" authorityYear="1909" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. grisea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="grisea">
<emphasis id="E148778330C03B809140924C5C8F449C" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus grisea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a wide distribution in south-eastern and southern-central France, ranging from Alpes-de-Haute-Provence and Hautes-Alpes to 
<normalizedToken id="BF8A5BB405FCA0B2B27D8FB306BCAE3D" originalValue="Isère">Isere</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="AC0383668EF48A8D9CFB8F19F7D0BD72" originalValue="Drôme">Drome</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="6D80725AB3718455E1755E0CA69DE443" originalValue="Ardèche">Ardeche</normalizedToken>
, Vaucluse, Aveyron, Lot and 
<normalizedToken id="C99637D991D6CE7F5590921B7B78222E" originalValue="Lozère">Lozere</normalizedToken>
. Based on phenotype (and geography - 
<taxonomicName id="9F73F7FDB295803B4CF74FFE57F6DD02" authorityName="Dujardin" authorityYear="1956" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. cleui" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="cleui">
<emphasis id="62407DCB686770CDF7126233DE92EEE3" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus cleui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
cannot be recognised as valid because its location is within the distributional range of 
<taxonomicName id="8C5E4C7FAE0FD3B1A9F810811DE962BA" authorityName="Oberthuer" authorityYear="1909" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. grisea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="grisea">
<emphasis id="ABFF08DF6F7CE61FF9C1B663701BD09D" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus grisea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), we see no justification for 
<bibRefCitation id="64C8780051F9706D0F09C88688EF3C92" author="Leraut, P" journalOrPublisher="NAP Editions, Verrieres-le Buisson" pageId="7" pageNumber="130" refId="B20" refString="Leraut, P, 2012. Volume 3: Moths of Europe, Zygaenids, Pyralids 1 and Brachodids. NAP Editions, Verrieres-le Buisson" title="Volume 3: Moths of Europe, Zygaenids, Pyralids 1 and Brachodids." year="2012">
<normalizedToken id="6E93236A09B517A3EF477B3F80FAF343" originalValue="Leraut’s">Leraut's</normalizedToken>
(2012
</bibRefCitation>
: 98) reinstatement of 
<taxonomicName id="6EB417999781A29CDC8F2C10394053C3" authorityName="Dujardin" authorityYear="1956" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. cleui" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="cleui">
<emphasis id="6F34197E3464FAD33AF27A641E42C2FE" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus cleui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a valid subspecies under which he placed 
<taxonomicName id="88FADA1AC154A31BC28E83189E1C9CB0" authorityName="Tremewan" authorityYear="1961" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. aragonia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="aragonia">
<emphasis id="9F8C37CB69AE8C8CCB1275F39A077515" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus aragonia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="5DE49677BAF5C439AE3AD2606642DAF6" authorityName="Mazel" authorityYear="1979" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. aurargentea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="aurargentea">
<emphasis id="1E6D8018545EFA26F9A7D284FEF7EF09" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus aurargentea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as synonyms (see also below). Even in the original description, Dujardin compared 
<taxonomicName id="3A74B0E55E4963A6888CCDD80CFBD6AE" authorityName="Dujardin" authorityYear="1956" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. cleui" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="cleui">
<emphasis id="D62FED57864D5845572BD9CE67BA580D" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus cleui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName id="7519B9B077CE7A26774F11D1686BD89F" authorityName="Oberthuer" authorityYear="1909" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. grisea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="grisea">
<emphasis id="A5BB3EAC644CBF89662F51F1CB595AB4" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus grisea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, stating that the forewing ground colour was similar. Consequently, it is here reinstated as a synonym (
<emphasis id="2E59DF635D93C41D62235ACDA8E5F967" bold="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">syn. rev.</emphasis>
) of 
<taxonomicName id="5A332CE8C61B9D2963520092967F4C91" authorityName="Oberthuer" authorityYear="1909" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena rhadamanthus subsp. grisea" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="rhadamanthus" subSpecies="grisea">
<emphasis id="73F651A067FAC9ACB3D43E6256C26A4C" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">Zygaena rhadamanthus grisea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as placed by 
<bibRefCitation id="E18F823CE31A89A0040E9DB7D50D3730" author="Hofmann, A" journalOrPublisher="Harley Books, Colchester" pageId="7" pageNumber="130" refId="B17" refString="Hofmann, A, Tremewan, WG, 1996. A systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae). Harley Books, Colchester" title="A systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae)." year="1996">Hofmann and Tremewan (1996</bibRefCitation>
: 131).
</paragraph>
